FBIS3-12070 "drlat061_c_94009" FBIS-LAT-94-061 Document Type:Daily Report 30 Mar 1994 MEXICO PAN Candidate on Zedillo Nomination PA3003020594 Mexico City Radio ACIR Network in Spanish 0000 GMT 30 Mar 94 PA3003020594 Mexico City Radio ACIR Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [From the "ACIR Radio News" newscast] [Text] Diego Fernandez de Zevallos, PAN [National Action Party] presidential candidate, has resumed his political campaign and said he is willing to fight for the Presidency with Ernesto Zedillo: [Begin Fernandez recording] Because of the public offices that Dr. Zedillo and I have held, I have had direct contact with him. He is a respectable man and politician. With his nomination by the PRI [Institutional Revolutionary Party] to replace Luis Donaldo Colosio -- rest in peace -- I again have an adversary, and I will fight for the Presidency of the republic. [end recording]
